## Conventions

- `role`: specific and descriptive (professional title)
- `goal`: result-oriented with `{input}` variable
- `backstory`: 2-3 sentences contextualizing expertise
- `max_iter`: limit iterations to prevent loops
- `memory=True` on Crew for cross-execution context
- `output_file` on last task to save result
- `Process.sequential` by default
- `Process.hierarchical` when a manager needs to decide order
- YAML for reusable configurations
